para.verbatim:
Generate docs/PERFORMANCE.md from strict benchmark JSON logs.
Key points: - Uses only the last 3 runs for each device. - Aggregations use tokens / time. - Includes Memory Details when present in per-run logs. - Includes a Deduplication section that reports *real* artifact sizes by following symlinks (reports target sizes, not link lengths).
